===1998=== The artists appearing at Lilith Fair varied by date (with McLachlan the only artist to play all dates).<ref name="Artists"/> Appearances were organized into three stages. Almost all Village Stage artists performed only one or two dates. Many of them won slots on the bill in a series of local talent searches in their home cities.
